Package: household-expense-tracker
Version: 2.0.0
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 18.0.0), postgresql (>= 12.0), postgresql-contrib
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Description: Household Expense Tracker Web Application
 A comprehensive household expense tracking web application with advanced
 financial management features, dark mode, and zero-configuration setup.
 .
 Features:
  - Expense management with categories
  - Split calculations between users
  - Analytics dashboard with charts
  - Data export (CSV/PDF)
  - Dark mode interface
  - Multi-year tracking
 .
 This package automatically configures PostgreSQL database and starts
 the web service on port 5000.
Homepage: https://github.com/your-username/household-expense-tracker